      "text": [
        " قَالَ رَسُولُ اللَّهِ ( صلى الله عليه وآله ) الْبِئْرُ جُبَارٌ وَ الْعَجْمَاءُ جُبَارٌ وَ الْمَعْدِنُ جُبَارٌ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "And by this chain, ",
          "He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘Rasool-Allah<sup>saww</sup> said: ‘(Being killed by) the well is ‘<span class=\"iTxt\">Jubarru</span>’, (no wergild for it), and (being killed by) the beasts, is ‘<span class=\"iTxt\">Jubarru</span>’ (no wergild for it), and (being killed by) the mines, is ‘<span class=\"iTxt\">Jubarru</span>’ (no wergild for it’."
        ]
      }
    }
